title: Complete coverage: Notre Dame defeats upset-minded Palisades, remains unbeaten
text:
Complete Box Score Â» 
Notre Dame remained unbeaten and on track for a huge Colonial League showdown with Saucon Valley next week with a 47-34 defeat of host Palisades Friday night. 
But the Crusaders (8-0) needed a spectacular night from junior running back/defensive back Mitch Daniel and some big plays to survive a ferocious upset bid from a driven bunch of Pirates (4-4). 
Follow the links below for complete coverage of the game.
